==English==
{{wikipedia}}

===Noun===
'''[[instrumental]] [[case]]'''

#{{grammar}}: noun [[case]] used to express [[means]] or [[agency]]—and is generally indicated in English by '''by''' or '''with''' with the objective. Languages that use the instrumental case include [[Croatian]], [[Czech]], [[Dyirbal]], [[Finnish]], [[Quechua]], [[Russian]] and [[Sanskrit]].

